  - Use Bootstrap Vue directives for form validation
  - Implement proper Bootstrap Vue component lifecycle

  # SCSS Styling
  - Use SCSS for styling with proper nesting
  - Follow BEM methodology for CSS classes
  - Use CSS custom properties for theming
  - Import global styles in main.js
  - Use scoped styles in components when appropriate

  # Icon Systems
  - Use Font Awesome icons as established in the project
  - Use Simple Line Icons for consistent iconography
  - Follow the established icon import patterns
  - Use proper icon sizing and styling

  # Theme Integration
  - Use the established color scheme and design system
  - Follow the precise-theme patterns
  - Implement responsive design patterns
  - Use the established spacing and typography patterns

  # Component Styling
  - Use Bootstrap classes for layout and spacing
  - Use CoreUI components for complex UI elements
  - Follow the established component styling patterns
  - Use proper CSS specificity and scoping

